{"tid":2489932,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家對十年前既放題有咩回憶","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:10:02.000Z","uid":80396,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ab15c319df5711c1885b6c2be47263aeffb823e3","tid":2489932,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.去兆萬間青葉。唔好食都係其次，份量真係吹脹。<br />\n魚生細細件食刀功，叫個牛肉鍋食諗住細細鍋好似吉野家咁試下啦，點知黎左個FULL SIZE既不銹鋼鍋連埋個FULL SIZE既爐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.第一次接觸放題係登打士街間2000円，心諗嘩百零蚊有甜蝦任食好抵呀。十年後諗起都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f3774cc42b69d6dacec29334fdb75dd560e0a3","tid":2489932,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:57:13.000Z","msg":"大B哥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f4cf52d77324d6ed962c02bda570d6abf1231d","tid":2489932,"uid":38904,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"細個覺得好抵食<br />\n大個發現係劣食"},{"pid":"696b7f7fb2a9b064bb6f255f461d98e385630bd9","tid":2489932,"uid":281492,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"吉壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4913aaf3f552d9a069cf79fa8ef44